t;Rareminds works to identify the gaps in employability &amp;amp; learning and over the years provide solutions to schools, colleges &amp;amp; corporates through various curated programs. From inadequacy of continual learning amongst individuals to change in work life priorities, we have constantly evolved and believe that no program is plug and play. Everyone is unique.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;text-muted&quot;&gt;Our experiences are with wide industry verticals to support their recruitment needs. Our Association with companies like IBM, Accenture, Publicis Sapient, Shriram Properties, Bounce, 6th Energy, Mahindra Aerospace, Futuregroup, Jaguar, Quickrides are few to mention. We work with educational institutions like Dayanand Sagar, Dr.AIT, East West College, Dairy College, Ryan International, St.Josephs School,CBSE, KJG to support them for various outcomes. To transform and enable deployability for corproates across technologies, or through design of experiential content and deliver futuristic specific programs to enhance employability across institutions.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;text-muted&quot;&gt;Our journey started with Individual development but over the years, our evolved capabilities of constant innovation and consistent development has driven us to expand. Our end to end solutions aimed at driving excellence across the education space; has today made us the most preferred choice not just by Individuals but also by Educational institutions across India.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;text-muted&quot;&gt;As your business partner, we work to achieve outcomes defined for each project that we sign up. Rareminds recognises the inadequacy of continuous learning and inability to recall to apply in real time. The individuals either need to be able to perform monotonous tasks, or to plan and strategize using theories, real-time data, statistics etc. &amp;amp; head the implementation to success. Most monotonous tasks are automated or there are ways to automate through and by 2040 a lot of jobs will be replaced by robots. There will be a lack of inequality in pay scales, creating further disruptions in the talent market. At Rareminds, services are curated for on-demand recruitment and learning. We bring out the balance between the Talent a company needs &amp;amp; priorities on individual experiences&lt;/p&gt;',NULL,'government/about',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2024-08-06 00:00:00','2024-09-05 18:01:05','About Rareminds - Government','Learn about Rareminds commitment to excellence in providing specialized services tailored for government organizations, driving innovation and success.','about, government, services, innovation','About Rareminds - Government','Explore Rareminds commitment to excellence in providing specialized services tailored for government organizations, driving innovation and success.'),(58,2,43,'Vision','',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'Prioritizing the needs and satisfaction of customers.',NULL,'',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2024-08-06 00:00:00','2024-09-05 18:02:10','About Rareminds - Corporate','Explore Rareminds mission to revolutionize corporate performance through innovative solutions tailored to drive growth, efficiency and success.','about, corporate, mission, innovation','About Rareminds - Corporate','Discover Rareminds mission to revolutionize corporate performance through innovative solutions tailored to drive growth, efficiency and success.'),(59,3,43,'Our Story',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'&lt;h3 class=&quot;mb-4&quot;&gt;Started in the year 2000, An organization founded by a woman, that grew to be led by a team of women and creating ripples in &lt;span class=&quot;text-primary&quot;&gt;talent experience space&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;blockquote class=&quot;blockquote&quot;&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;mb-0&quot;&gt;Rareminds works to identify the gaps in employability &amp;amp; learning and over the years provide solutions to schools, colleges &amp;amp; corporates through vario